course_description = '<div class="richtext richtext__medium"> <div class="lede">If you have an idea about the course you''d like to study with us and want a more supportive approach, the Diploma of University Studies is for you.</div><p>The Diploma of University Studies focuses on specialised units relevant to the course you''re interested in. You''ll learn key skills and build knowledge that will help you to succeed in your chosen pathway. The units you study in this course can also be credited into your Bachelor degree.</p><p>The course is offered full time or part-time. Campus, semester and attendance mode availability varies by specialisation - please refer to the table below.</p><table border="1" id="table58177" style="width: 100%;"><thead><tr><th id="table58177r1c1" style="text-align: left;">Specialisation</th><th id="table58177r1c2" style="text-align: left;">Availability</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r2c1" style="text-align: left;">Arts</th><td headers="table58177r1c2 table58177r2c1"><p>Semester 1: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p><p>Semester 2: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p></td></tr><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r3c1" style="text-align: left;">Business</th><td headers="table58177r1c2 table58177r3c1"><p>Semester 1: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p><p>Semester 2: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p></td></tr><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r4c1" style="text-align: left;">Education</th><td headers="table58177r1c2 table58177r4c1"><p>Semester 1: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p><p>Semester 2: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p><p><em>Note: Availability of pathway options within specialisation may be limited dependent on choice of location. Please see the course structure section for specific information.</em></p></td></tr><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r5c1" style="text-align: left;">Engineering</th><td headers="table58177r1c2 table58177r5c1"> Semester 1: Hobart and Launceston </td></tr><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r6c1" style="text-align: left;"> Health Science</th><td headers="table58177r1c2 table58177r6c1"> Semester 1: Hobart and Launceston </td></tr><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r7c1" style="text-align: left;">Science</th><td headers="table58177r1c2 table58177r7c1"><p>Semester 1: Cradle Coast, Hobart and Launceston</p><p>Semester 2: Cradle Coast, Hobart and Launceston</p><p><em>Note: Availability of pathway options within specialisation may be limited dependent on choice of location. Please see the course structure section for specific information.</em></p></td></tr><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r8c1" style="text-align: left;"> Nursing Foundation Studies</th><td headers="table58177r1c2 table58177r8c1"> Semester 1: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Rozelle – Sydney </td></tr><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r9c1" style="text-align: left;"> Paramedicine Foundation Studies</th><td headers="table58177r1c2 table58177r9c1"> Semester 1: Hobart and Rozelle – Sydney </td></tr><tr style="text-align: left;"><th id="table58177r10c1" style="text-align: left;">Psychology</th><td headers="table58177r10c1 table58177r1c2"><p>Semester 1: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p><p>Semester 2: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p></td></tr><tr><th id="table58177r11c1" style="text-align: left;"> Social Work</th><td headers="table58177r11c1 table58177r1c2"><p>Semester 1: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p><p>Semester 2: Cradle Coast, Hobart, Launceston and Online</p></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="table__responsive"></div><hr/><h5>Watch our course information webinar</h5><p>Thinking of studying this course and want to learn more? This webinar explores course structures, career opportunities, and the student experience to support your study journey.</p><p><a href=