course_description = '<div class="richtext richtext__medium"> <h6>Are you passionate about the great outdoors?</h6><div class="lede">Our first-of-its-kind diploma is designed for those dedicated to making a positive impact on the environment, and eager to lead others on a journey towards a more sustainable future.</div><p>Our course offers you a unique blend of academic study and hands-on experience in one of the planet’s most ecologically diverse regions. You’ll explore the rugged mountains, tranquil forests, and breathtaking coastlines, using Tasmania’s natural beauty as a dynamic classroom for your outdoor adventures and learning experiences. By participating in practical fieldwork experiences, you''ll directly apply your knowledge in real-world scenarios, thereby contributing to addressing environmental challenges on both local and global scales.</p><p>If you''re passionate about nature and adventure, this practical diploma is for you. It can help you advance in your current career, provide a pathway to outdoor and environment-related employment, and build your ability to inspire and empower others in a range of professional and personal endeavours.</p><hr/><h5>Watch our course information webinar</h5><p>Thinking of studying this course in 2025 and want to learn more? This webinar explores course structures, career opportunities, and the student experience to support your study journey.</p><p><a href="https://youtu.be/XbnqVubUnfo" target="_blank" title="Watch our webinar">Watch now</a></p> </div>',
