course_description = '<div class="richtext richtext__medium"> <div class="lede">The first of its kind in Australia, the Graduate Certificate in Organisational Resilience offers a holistic approach to understanding and applying organisational resilience. Developed in collaboration with leading resilience researchers and informed by national and international industry partners across public, private, and not-for-profit sectors, this course equips students with both theoretical knowledge and practitioner-relevant skills.</div><p>This fully online course is designed for professionals seeking to lead and implement change across diverse sectors. It provides the flexibility to study individual units as short courses or complete the full graduate certificate. Graduates will be well-positioned to pursue roles in organisational resilience, crisis management, protective security, and business continuity management.</p> </div>',
