UPDATE courses SET
course_description = '<div class="richtext richtext__medium"> <div class="lede">The Bachelor of Business at the University of Tasmania offers a learning experience that is deeply connected to place, purpose, and possibility. Set against the backdrop of one of the world’s most pristine environments, this degree equips you with the knowledge and skills to thrive in complex, evolving markets — both locally and globally.</div><p>You’ll explore Tasmania’s growing industries, including energy, agriculture, and tourism, and learn to navigate the current economic climate through real-world projects and data-driven decision-making. Guided by leading researchers and supported by insights from industry professionals, you’ll gain practical experience in areas such as financial and investment analysis, corporate advisory, and investment banking.</p><p><strong>Study Business Where Innovation Meets Nature</strong></p><ul><li>Direct exposure to Tasmania’s key industries and economic challenges</li><li>Real-world learning using actual data and live business projects</li><li>Guest lectures and webinars from local and international industry leaders</li><li>A strong focus on sustainability, ethics, and Indigenous perspectives</li><li>Smaller class sizes and greater access to academic and industry mentors</li><li>A lifestyle like no other — with 40% of the island protected as national parks, reserves, and world heritage areas</li></ul><p>A Bachelor of Business gives you the skills to turn your passion into a career. With the flexibility to customise your degree, you’re able to choose between several majors to suit your personal and professional interests and ambitions. Our connections with industry give you a real-world advantage.</p><p>This degree can be combined to form a double degree. <a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/study/undergraduate/double-degrees">Explore your options</a> and find out how you can accelerate your career.</p><!-- START CS NO INDEX --><div><div class="table__respo