UPDATE courses SET
course_description = '<div class="richtext richtext__medium"> <div class="lede">A research degree is an advanced study program that gives you an opportunity to deeply explore a topic with the support and expertise of your supervisors.</div><p paraeid="{979bb505-656f-4906-b974-bee6dcd78489}{248}" paraid="2076845606">As a Research Masters student, you will conduct independent research in a specialised field to gain advanced and integrated understanding of a complex body of knowledge and gain the knowledge and skills to apply that knowledge with autonomy, expert judgement, adaptability and responsibility. You will be provided with training activities and career development opportunities to develop high-level research, communication and project management skills. The knowledge and skills obtained from a Masters will set you up for success as a practitioner or learner in your chosen field and for a wide range of future career opportunities.</p><p paraeid="{5d8e47ce-d532-42ca-87ec-9736f9b33ba4}{23}" paraid="166929369">Please see the <a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/research/degrees/available-projects" rel="noreferrer noopener">Available Projects</a> page to explore our Higher Degree by Research projects, specific eligibility criteria and opportunities for scholarship support. Learn more about some of our supervisors <a href="https://discover.utas.edu.au" rel="noreferrer noopener">discover.utas.edu.au</a></p><p paraeid="{5d8e47ce-d532-42ca-87ec-9736f9b33ba4}{59}" paraid="1663248148">Visit the links below for detailed information about:</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/research/degrees/scholarships-and-fees"><strong>Scholarships and Fees</strong></a></li><li><a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/research/degrees"><strong>Application Process</strong></a></li><li><a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/research/degrees/what-is-a-research-degree"><strong>Entry Requirements</strong> <strong>and Research Degrees</strong></a></li></ul> </div>',
