r have experience equivalent to a satisfactory achievement in the following Tasmanian Senior Secondary subject:</p> <ul> <li>Chemistry (CHM415115)</li> </ul> <p>You can <a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/enquire?seedData=%25asset_web_path%25">enquire online</a> for information on interstate and international equivalents to the Tasmanian senior secondary subject above. If you need assistance to meet the prerequisite, we offer <a href="https://www.utas.edu.au/foundation-units">foundation units</a> that you can complete before you start your course.</p> <p> </p> </div>',
